data.description: Take a look at this charming brick home! Here is a 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a fireplace in the River Oaks subdivision. Several recent upgrades to the home include a spacious updated kitchen with tons of cabinets and good counter top space, all new appliances less than 2 months old, plus a roof less than 1.5 years old, new hot water heater, Nest thermostat, and updated showers.  Sitting on a larger oversized lot this property offers room for a garden and space for the kiddos to run and play. Fenced off into 2 separate yard spaces you have several opportunities for the space. There are 3 nice sheds, plus one is fully insulated and has electricity and currently used as a kid cave. Also staying with the property is the above ground pool with all the equipment to run and maintain it.
